parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment or inadvertent deployment of airbags, which can cause serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: the airbag does not deploy in a crash
cracks in the dashboard around the airbag area
the passenger side airbag sensor fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall issues can cause the airbag to deploy improperly, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: the dealer informs the owner that the repair might cause the dashboard to crack
the owner is required to sign a waiver to ensure the dealer is not held responsible for any damages to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard around the airbag area can cause the airbag to deploy improperly, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Cracks in the dashboard around the airbag area
the crack is in a corner of the deployment zone
the dashboard is cracked in an area above the gauges.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking or fracturing of the dashboard can lead to a compromised airbag system, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Cracks or fractures on the dashboard
particularly on the passenger side above the airbag
or on the driver side from the base of the windshield to the top of the instrument cluster.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handles can make it impossible to open the doors of the vehicle, which can lead to safety risks, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: Door handles come off on the driver and passenger doors
making it impossible to open the doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the frame can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, which can lead to safety risks, especially in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Rust covering the frame of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leaking of the third brake light can cause water to enter the vehicle, which can lead to electrical issues, corrosion, and safety risks.
symptoms: Water comes in around the back window from the third brake light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a loss of power, which can lead to safety risks, especially when towing a trailer.
symptoms: Loss of power to the trailer
